Basic Structure :
  - Create a home page where all the blog links are displayed.
  - Create a user sign-up system so they can create blogs too.
  - Use PostgreSQL for backend purpose.
  - Serialize the blog metadata when inserting to database.


Website Related :
  - Make multi-pages website.
  - Use good-for-the-eyes color scheme.
  - Make Tags and a blog filtering system via tags.
  - Give user the ability to add a thumbnail/art to add to their blog.


Core Things To Keep In Mind :
  - Make a logging system to log all error/warnings/info.
  - Use elaborate error handling.
  - Serialize ALL data when inserting to database.
  - If possible, use async-PostgreSQL for asynchronous db run.
  - Optimize the flask website as much as possible.
